description: Permanently deletes a SqlInjectionMatchSet. You can't delete a SqlInjectionMatchSet if it's still used in any Rules or if it still contains any SqlInjectionMatchTuple objects. If you just want to remove a SqlInjectionMatchSet from a Rule, use UpdateRule. To permanently delete a SqlInjectionMatchSet from AWS WAF, perform the following steps:   Update the SqlInjectionMatchSet to remove filters, if any. For more information, see UpdateSqlInjectionMatchSet.   Use GetChangeToken to get the change token that you provide in the ChangeToken parameter of a DeleteSqlInjectionMatchSet request.   Submit a DeleteSqlInjectionMatchSet request.
